          <strong>First</strong> - you should answer the initial questions. 
          <%= link_to "Click here", new_question_path, class: 'button-link' %>
        </li>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group col-md-12">
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>Second</strong> - you should enter information of all the credit card debts you carry. 
          <%= link_to "Click here", new_credit_card_debt_path, class: 'button-link' %>
          </li>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group col-md-12">
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>Third</strong> - you should enter informatino of all other consumer debts you carry. 
          <%= link_to "Click here", new_consumer_debt_path, class: 'button-link' %>
        </li>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group col-md-12">
        <li class="list-group-item">
          We will take care of the rest from there.
        </li>
      </div>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
